{
  "texts": [
    "Responses are first generated greedily with up to 1024 tokens (default value for MT Bench).",
    "The responses to these prompts are evaluated by GPT-4-0125-Preview to give a score between 1 and 10, and the mean across all prompts is reported.",
    "Prompts in Coding, Math and Reasoning categories are evaluated with a reference correct answer, which were generated by the judge model and then manually verified to be correct.",
    "Higher MT Bench score indicates better instruction following ability.",
    "AlpacaEval 2.0 Length Controlled We follow Dong et al. (2024); Meng et al."
  ]
